video.title: 666 Park Avenue
video.synopsis: The residents of a historic building in Manhattan can get anything they desire -- but a Faustian price will be exacted by a dark supernatural force.

episodes.synopsis: Jane and Henry are the new managers at New York's most seductive address. But the residents, including the building's owners, give them the creeps.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: Jane makes a terrifying discovery about what lies behind the walls of The Drake as she begins to renovate Mr. Barlow's apartment.
episodes.title: Murmurations

episodes.synopsis: More mysteries begin to unfold at The Drake as Jane repeatedly glimpses a little girl who beckons her to a room with a strange suitcase.
episodes.title: The Dead Don't Stay Dead

episodes.synopsis: When Henry learns that Gavin is under investigation, he must choose between loyalty to his boss or his friendship with Gavin.
episodes.title: Hero Complex

episodes.synopsis: As Olivia puts the finishing touches on the lobby for the annual Drake Halloween costume gala, it brings to mind a memorable Halloween night in 1929.
episodes.title: A Crowd of Demons

episodes.synopsis: Traumatized by the terror she experienced at the Dorans' party, Jane is even more devastated by the lack of support from detectives -- and from Henry.
episodes.title: Diabolic

episodes.synopsis: Henry's political career continues to rise. However his exultation is tempered by Jane's ever-deepening dismay about staying at The Drake.
episodes.title: Downward Spiral

episodes.synopsis: When Jane disappears without a trace, Henry worries for her safety and sanity. Meanwhile, Gavin has Victor held captive in The Drake's boiler room.
episodes.title: Whatever Happened to Baby Jane?

episodes.synopsis: Jane is hurled back in time to 1927 by the mysterious Maris Elder, who hypnotizes her to find out where she disappeared down the spiral staircase.
episodes.title: Hypnos

episodes.synopsis: Henry questions his future in politics. Meanwhile, Jane seeks the key that will decrypt the diary, and she has to find a hidden door in the building.
episodes.title: The Comfort of Death

episodes.synopsis: Henry's political career is in the palm of Sasha's hand. Louise's relapse upsets Brian, while at the same time Alexis plots her revenge on Louise.
episodes.title: Sins of the Fathers

episodes.synopsis: Jane tries to learn more about the "conspiratii" mentioned in the diary. Henry searches for Jane's father, and Alexis and Louise face off.
episodes.title: The Elysian Fields

episodes.synopsis: Louise and Brian have trouble hiding the body. Jane's father returns and tries to take her away at gunpoint as he reveals the truth about her past.
episodes.title: Lazarus: Part 1
